failure to stop when brakes are applied

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Fuel leaks and fires can cause serious accidents, injuries, or fatalities, and may lead to vehicle damage or total loss.
symptoms: wisps of smoke coming from under the hood
and fires starting under the hood.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Head Gasket Leaks and Engine Oil Leaks
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Head gasket leaks and engine oil leaks can cause engine damage, overheating, and potentially lead to fires or accidents.
symptoms: wisps of smoke coming from under the hood

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Hesitation or surging when accelerating can cause accidents, loss of control, or near-miss situations.
symptoms: Hesitation when accelerating from a stop
surging or revving when letting off the gas

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the air bag control module can lead to failure of air bags to deploy in the event of an accident, potentially causing injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Passenger side air bag off light illuminating
failure of air bags to deploy
and failure of the occupant detection sensor.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Stalling and Failure to Start
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine stalling and failure to start can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities, especially in situations where the vehicle is in motion or in traffic.
symptoms: and requiring priming of the ignition switch to start the engine.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the front control arm can cause loss of control of the vehicle, leading to accidents, damage, and potential injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Sudden breakage of the control arm
rust or corrosion on the control arm.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause loss of steering control, making it difficult or impossible to steer the vehicle, leading to accidents or damage.
symptoms: Power steering failure warning light illuminated
extra effort required to turn the steering wheel

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Corrosion and rust on the control arms can lead to sudden failure, causing loss of control of the vehicle and potential accidents or damage.

sudden breakage of the control arm.
